Visa Ndani ya Biblia respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our mobile application.

1. Information We Collect
Visa Ndani ya Biblia does not collect any personal data, including names, email addresses, or phone numbers. The app is designed to provide you with Bible-related content without requiring any personal information from you.

2. Data Usage and Sharing
Since we do not collect personal data, Visa Ndani ya Biblia does not use, share, or sell any personal information to third parties. We do not track your usage of the app or collect any data related to your activities within the app.

3. Advertising
Our app may display third-party advertisements to support the appâ€™s development and maintenance. These ads are provided by third-party ad networks, which may collect non-personal data such as your device's IP address, location, and browsing habits to display targeted ads. Visa Ndani ya Biblia does not have access to this information.

Ad Providers
Google AdMob: We use Google AdMob to serve ads in the app. For more information about how Google AdMob collects and uses data, please refer to the Google AdMob Privacy Policy.
4. Security
We are committed to maintaining the security of your data. Although we do not collect personal data, we strive to protect the integrity of any data processed by third-party ad providers.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The latest version will always be available on this page.

